<br>
Needless to say i sat there for over an hour with my mouth opened as i watched the second plane hit, then the reports from the pentagon, and the plane crash in PA<br>
<br>
I finaly went down to have breakfast and the workers down there hadn't heard anything...it was hard for me to tell them the news.<br>
<br>
Later that day there were a couple FBI agents walking around with the Dean, and the campus police.<br>
<br>
That day will be forever etched in my mind.  I remember when i was 10 visiting the WTC and looking out across the city, wish i could have gone back before this happened.<br>
